{"tid":582333,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一列火車上，坐著一位泰國人、一位韓國人，一位台灣教授以及一個台灣大學生。","createTime":"2018-03-06T05:39:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T07:23:30.000Z","uid":135695,"like":76,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8cf10be3fb930f27eb86d9db5a7b09b88f03f45e","tid":582333,"uid":135695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T05:39:17.000Z","msg":"一列火車上，坐著一位泰國人、一位韓國人，一位台灣教授以及一個台灣大學生。<br />\n途中，泰國人拿出幾顆榴槤分給大家吃，然後將剩下幾顆往窗外丟。<br />\n<br />\n「你這樣不是太浪費了嗎？」台灣教授問<br />\n<br />\n「泰國有的是榴槤&hellip;　」泰國人驕傲地說<br />\n「我們根本吃不完。」<br />\n<br />\n不多久，韓國人也拿出幾株高級人蔘分給大家吃，但他自己吃沒幾口就把它扔了。<br />\n<br />\n台灣教授驚訝地問：<br />\n「這可是上好的人蔘！怎麼扔了咧？！」<br />\n<br />\n韓國人不在乎地說：<br />\n「我們韓國有的是人蔘，怎麼吃也吃不完。」<br />\n<br />\n台灣教授沉思了一會兒，然後突然站了起來，抱起身邊一起來的台灣大學生，然後硬把他塞<br />\n出了窗外&hellip;"},{"pid":"9ff7196a2949bb2006b9a2f51c72ffd1b1ddf7ae","tid":582333,"uid":125752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T05:42:52.000Z","msg":"哈哈哈 又幾盞鬼"},{"pid":"a0df0c53f349f9663e99236966f571a8a42e79fb","tid":582333,"uid":87339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T06:22:17.000Z","msg":"頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a57258875fdf87d99b075c27c3c2c9b29994ad8d","tid":582333,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T06:25:59.000Z","msg":"車上有無中國人？"},{"pid":"4f6dc537749ef12cc82ed65d0a57b08cd484cfbe","tid":582333,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T06:27:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dea744b4de23592805c5a00105a2e04d6e135cfd","tid":582333,"uid":35248,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"a57258875fdf87d99b075c27c3c2c9b29994ad8d","tid":582333,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T06:25:59.000Z","msg":"車上有無中國人？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T06:40:5